{
  "episode_id": "2026-07-18",
  "chunks": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "听众朋友大家好，欢迎收听AI 每日先锋，今天是2026年7月18日。我是苏晴。",
      "start": 1.0,
      "duration": 6.922,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_001_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_001_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "大家好，我是周航。",
      "start": 8.371,
      "duration": 1.48,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_002_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_002_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "周航你昨天熬夜看了没？Google那个Antigravity 2.0直接给我看傻了，这回是真的把Agent给\"端\"到桌面上来了。",
      "start": 10.348,
      "duration": 9.361,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_003_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_003_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "我跟你说，这事儿我在官方博客翻了好久才搞明白它到底牛在哪。<breath> 很多人一听\"桌面端Agent\"就想着\"哦，跟ChatGPT电脑客户端似的呗\"，那可就太小看DeepMind了。",
      "start": 20.162,
      "duration": 13.777,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_004_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_004_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "对对对，我一开始也这么想的，你给我讲讲。",
      "start": 34.344,
      "duration": 2.743,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_005_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_005_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "传统的AI产品是什么形态？是你打开一个聊天框，然后想办法跟模型交互，对吧？你是中心，模型是工具。<laughing>但Antigravity 2.0完全反过来了——你是任务提出者，Agent接管整个工作流。</laughing>它覆盖macOS、Linux、Windows三大系统，这意味着不管你用什么电脑，都能跑同一套Agent体验。",
      "start": 37.52,
      "duration": 23.375,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_006_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_006_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "等等，这听起来不就是年初各家都在吹的\"自主Agent\"嘛，有啥本质区别？",
      "start": 61.36,
      "duration": 6.531,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_007_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_007_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "你注意啊，关键在<strong>\"原生\"</strong>这两个字。之前很多所谓的Agent功能，其实是聊天框加插件的缝合怪，你得自己串流程。<breath> 但Antigravity 2.0是把任务规划、工具调用、多步推理从架构层面就揉在一起了，不是外挂，是长在骨头里的。",
      "start": 68.353,
      "duration": 20.961,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_008_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_008_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "那对我们普通人来说到底意味着什么？我以后打开电脑，是不是就不需要自己点软件了？",
      "start": 89.765,
      "duration": 7.967,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_009_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_009_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "往这个方向走是没错的。举个例子，你现在想做一个季度汇报，可能得打开Word写文档、Excel做图表、PPT排版、发邮件给领导。<laughing>那未来你可能就一句话丢过去，Agent自己拆解步骤，跨应用给你跑完了。</laughing>个人生产力软件的格局，估计要被重新洗一遍。",
      "start": 98.232,
      "duration": 22.006,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_010_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_010_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "我的天，这画面也太赛博了。不过话说回来，我有点担心，万一Agent自己乱点东西把我文件删了咋办？",
      "start": 120.676,
      "duration": 9.012,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_011_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_011_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "这就是为什么DeepMind在多步规划和权限控制上要下大功夫。说白了，Agent能不能让人放心，核心不是它有多聪明，而是它的边界够不够清晰。",
      "start": 130.149,
      "duration": 11.712,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_012_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_012_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "行，谷歌这边先告一段落。对了还有件事儿，WAIC 2026上商汤那个\"算电协同Agent\"你关注了没？",
      "start": 142.306,
      "duration": 10.057,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_013_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_013_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "关注了，这事儿我觉得比模型本身还值得聊。<strong>单位电力Token产出提升80%</strong>，这个数字你乍一听是不是以为是搞新能源的？",
      "start": 152.837,
      "duration": 11.015,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_014_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_014_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "真的假的？做AI的突然开始卷电力成本了？<laughter>",
      "start": 164.279,
      "duration": 4.702,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_015_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_015_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "这就是2026年的趋势，AI算力已经逼近能源瓶颈了。你注意啊，GPU可以买、可以扩，但电不是你想用多少就有多少的。<breath> 商汤的思路是把算力调度升级成\"算电协同\"，相当于给每个推理任务都建了一个电费模型，让系统自动选择最省电的时段和节点去跑。",
      "start": 169.445,
      "duration": 22.702,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_016_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_016_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "那这80%是咋来的？是硬件升级还是纯算法优化？",
      "start": 192.564,
      "duration": 5.486,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_017_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_017_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "主要是调度层面的耦合优化。简单来说，之前大家只想着怎么让GPU利用率更高，现在商汤告诉你，<laughing>让一百度电跑出更多Token，比让一块卡满载更重要。</laughing> 因为电价是有波峰的波谷的，推理任务可以挪到便宜的时段跑，硬件本身不变，产出就上去了。",
      "start": 198.486,
      "duration": 22.31,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_018_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_018_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "懂了，这就是\"把每度电榨干\"。那这对行业意味着啥？",
      "start": 221.213,
      "duration": 5.834,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_019_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_019_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "说白了，下一代IDC的定价权，可能不在谁有更多显卡，而在谁能把电用得更精。谁掌握这套协同调度，谁的推理成本就能压到最低，到时候云服务报价就完全不一样了。",
      "start": 227.543,
      "duration": 15.543,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_020_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_020_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "这也太关键了，以前大家卷模型参数，现在开始卷电费单了是吧？",
      "start": 243.498,
      "duration": 6.226,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_021_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_021_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "可以这么理解。<laughing>所以我说2026年AI的关键词是\"落地\"，不是单纯的模型多强，而是整个基础设施能不能扛得住。</laughing>",
      "start": 250.203,
      "duration": 11.973,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_022_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_022_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "行，那趁热打铁，说几则快讯。第一个，面壁智能开源了个叫StaffDeck的东西，给AI发工号、定岗位、做绩效，<laughing>我看到这消息第一反应是——AI终于要交社保了吗？</laughing>",
      "start": 262.608,
      "duration": 20.438,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_023_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_023_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "哈哈你这个角度够刁钻。不过StaffDeck确实有意思，它解决的是一个很实际的问题：数字员工现在能干活了，但怎么管理？传统HR那一套能不能套用到AI身上？",
      "start": 283.514,
      "duration": 13.322,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_024_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_024_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "对啊，怎么个管理法？给AI打绩效打分？",
      "start": 297.326,
      "duration": 3.352,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_025_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_025_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "你注意啊，它的思路是给AI Agent建立完整的HR闭环。<breath> 从入职（模型加载）、岗位分配（任务路由）、到绩效评估（完成率、质量评分），全部数字化。<strong>这意味着数字员工第一次具备了\"组织化生存\"的资格</strong>，不再是临时工，而是有\"工号\"的正式员工。",
      "start": 301.155,
      "duration": 20.003,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_026_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_026_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "话说，这会不会让一些公司悄悄用AI替换掉初级岗位？",
      "start": 321.576,
      "duration": 4.963,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_027_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_027_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "这是个很现实的问题。但反过来想，有了StaffDeck这种框架，企业反而能更清楚地知道AI干了什么、效果如何、合规与否。<laughing>从\"摸着石头过河\"变成\"有据可查\"，至少管理上是透明的。</laughing>",
      "start": 326.978,
      "duration": 16.999,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_028_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_028_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "说得也是。好，下一个，沐曦在WAIC展台集结了十大开源社区，号称\"每个Token背后都是开源协作\"。",
      "start": 344.389,
      "duration": 11.494,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_029_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_029_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "沐曦这步棋走得挺聪明。国产GPU现在最大的短板不是硬件性能，是生态——开发者愿不愿意在你的卡上跑代码、贡献工具链。",
      "start": 356.376,
      "duration": 10.623,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_030_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_030_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "那拉开源社区站台，是不是就想解决这个问题？",
      "start": 367.408,
      "duration": 4.702,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_031_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_031_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "对。<breath> 你看英伟达之所以牢不可破，不是因为GPU硬件多牛，而是CUDA生态绑死了所有人。沐曦现在做的事就是从\"开源叙事\"切入，告诉社区\"来我这儿贡献，你的代码能在国产卡上跑出价值\"，用社区力量反哺生态。",
      "start": 372.597,
      "duration": 19.219,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_032_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_032_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "这事儿对咱们开发者有啥实际好处？",
      "start": 392.258,
      "duration": 2.961,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_033_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_033_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "好处是选择多了。之前大家要么CUDA要么没得选，现在至少有了一条\"国产+开源\"的备选路径。<laughing>虽然短期内CUDA还是主流，但生态这东西，五年后什么样谁说得准呢。</laughing>",
      "start": 395.679,
      "duration": 15.78,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_034_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_034_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "没错。最后一条，达卯科技发布算电协同2.0，推出AIDC绿电直连能源运营操作系统，说白了就是让数据中心\"算随电走\"。",
      "start": 411.93,
      "duration": 12.582,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_035_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_035_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "这个概念挺有意思的。\"算随电走\"和\"算电协同\"听着差不多，其实角度不同。<breath> 商汤那个是把任务往便宜电调度，达卯这个是让数据中心的算力跟着绿电的供给走——哪儿风电光伏富余，算力就往哪儿流动。",
      "start": 424.924,
      "duration": 16.738,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_036_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_036_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "那这不是得把机房建到戈壁滩上去？",
      "start": 442.107,
      "duration": 3.352,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_037_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_037_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "没错，未来AI基础设施可能要重新选址了。传统IDC扎堆大城市是因为延迟低，但大城市的电贵且不绿。<laughing>现在算电协同2.0要做的是打破这个假设，让算力可以跟着能源走。</laughing>",
      "start": 445.914,
      "duration": 17.26,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_038_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_038_lively.mp3"
      },
